{"tid":1111171,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"其實抽水呢個行為算唔算落井下石？","createTime":"2019-04-16T22:09:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-17T05:48:37.000Z","uid":167326,"like":29,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"4393f0e2be8357609d17905c3f89534c7f19d14c","tid":1111171,"uid":167326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T22:09:07.000Z","msg":"睇左成日安心 開始對抽水呢個行為有啲反感 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然唔知佢地背後有咩理由原因想偷食 但就因為係公眾人物 所以成件事比全港當花生食 <br />\n當事人又好無辜嘅人都好 都比人抽哂水 感覺好可憐 好落井下石 睇人仆街最開心咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實係咪得我一個咁奇怪 呢啲事我真係抽唔落水 好撚慘 <br />\n<br />\n一睇到啲關公開po抽水 尤其是狗巴 本身形象麻麻 仲要咁樣懶好笑抽水法 我覺得更加cheap<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FoMCPEj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFoMCPEj.png&h=3587ba69&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"351bcd1d7569515e2f32a89c2617725c58629a54","tid":1111171,"uid":167326,"like":12,"dislike":6,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T22:13:02.000Z","msg":"仲有呢啲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我愈睇愈心酸 明明冇做錯事嘅馬明 都要比全港市民係度撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/53fssrV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F53fssrV.png&h=4d28c56d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6c5ae720a0d79c3a2fa42ecb03a3b2d89096bfde","tid":1111171,"uid":245922,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T22:28:38.000Z","msg":"十個po九個都講緊佢地 我真係費時禁入去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bbf2acbe779ac29c7a269ef20fcfc8cb38581ab","tid":1111171,"uid":167326,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6c5ae720a0d79c3a2fa42ecb03a3b2d89096bfde","tid":1111171,"uid":245922,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"